{"tid":895680,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我想訓教姐！點解d仆街蚊唔肯放過我啊！","createTime":"2018-11-09T11:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T01:07:22.000Z","uid":24436,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2213484f64f2e9468351a12602d328d8bc71b138","tid":895680,"uid":24436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T11:32:17.000Z","msg":"屋企住低層，咁岩平台對正下面有個小花園<br />\n所以呢排一唔開冷氣就勁撚多蚊<br />\n<br />\nD仆街蚊真係好撚煩 <br />\n針到你豬頭咁，d蚊爛鬼死咁大粒都算<br />\n仲要係你耳邊飛黎飛去，嘈到你無教好訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家晚晚起碼殺3隻，但係發覺長此落去唔係辦法<br />\n日日返工都無精神<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲打有良策<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n液態蚊香有無用？<br />\n殺他殺 定 雷達個隻好用？<br />\n同埋係咪唔可以開太耐？<br />\n係咪會對人體有害？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係有其他產品好用？麻煩咁多位推薦下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nThanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4c131a7c952f83179fe038fe23a4b564f8c921","tid":895680,"uid":24436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T11:32:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be496796929de615235547211e4c1fc9c64420b","tid":895680,"uid":24436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T11:33:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"437ec635b671ab609d5a8562a0f939731a471238","tid":895680,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T11:33:39.000Z","msg":"裝蚊帳"},{"pid":"2f3aacc5bab1a89b8cf6246a15377b29f58ac495","tid":895680,"uid":13395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci